quran[9{c,v,t}:
33,7,aur jab hum ne payghambaroon se ehad liya aur tum se Nooh se aur ibrahim se aur moose se aur maryam ke betay eesa se. aur ehad bhi unn se pakka liya
33,8,taakay sach kehnay walon se unn ki sachaai ke baray mein daryaft kere aur is ne kafiroon ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
33,9,momino khuda ki uss meharbani ko yaad karo jo ( uss ne ) tum par ( uss waqt ki ) jab faujein tum par ( hamla karne ko ) ayen. to hum ne unn par howa bhaije aur aisay lashkar ( nazil kiye ) jin ko tum dekh nahi satke they. aur jo kaam tum karte ho khuda unn ko dekh raha hai
33,10,jab woh tumahray ooper aur neechay ki taraf se tum par charh aeye aur jab ankhen phir gayeen aur dil ( maaray dehshat ke ) gulon taq poanch gay aur tum khuda ki nisbat terhan terhan ke gumaan karne lagey
33,11,wahan momin aazamaa_e gay aur sakht tor par hlaye gay
33,12,aur jab munhafiq aur woh log jin ke dilon mein bemari hai kehnay lagey ke khuda aur is ke rasool ne hum se mehez dhokay ka wadakiya tha
33,13,aur jab unn mein se aik jamaat kehti thi ke ae ahal madinah ( yahan ) tumahray theharnay ka maqam nahi to lout chalo. aur aik giroh un mein se paighambar se ijazat mangnay aur kehnay laga ke hamaray ghar khulay parre hain halaank woh khulay nahi they. woh to sirf bhagna chahtay they
33,14,aur agar ( faujein ) atraaf madinah se un par aa daakhil hon phir unn se khanah jungi ke liye kaha jaye to ( foran ) karne lagen aur is ke liye bohat hi kam tawaquf karen
33,15,halaank pehlay khuda se iqraar kar chuke they ke peeth nahi phrin ge. aur khuda se ( jo ) iqraar (kiya jata hai uss ki ) zaroor prssh hogi
